{"tid":303200,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 落機拎喼，有人開過我個喼黎","createTime":"2017-06-30T03:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T04:04:47.000Z","uid":1303,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e32e5227c015b6c7036769638a462749525c4ca","tid":303200,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:42:24.000Z","msg":"1. 無論係喼本身個密碼鎖同橫綁條密碼鎖(防爆喼條帶)都直接去左我set個密碼個到，姐係一禁就開到。點解肯定唔會係自己大頭蝦，係因為我每次鎖喼都肯定check兩次，唔會犯呢個錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 打開個喼入面每個拉鍊都開晒，搞到啲野亂晒龍。呢樣更加肯定唔會係自己搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 未詳細點，但應該無唔見野。我亦無值錢野係入面，得生活用品呀衫呀小手信呀朱古力呀咁。唔排除少左條底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (好彩無多到野，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁啱我落機有比海關抽檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  )<br />\n<br />\n4. 最嬲係我啲朱古力碎撚晒，已經超過話撞兩野個種碎。而且我有包好佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 離開左機場先發現，都搵都唔知搵邊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求問 : <br />\n有無巴絲有類似經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 向咩機構查詢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次點防範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4ae7efc7fc1a609545d53c92f0ac4470421ef4","tid":303200,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796a5dc81a8bc3e0a41414da3d75eb1571fda695","tid":303200,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201a6cddd63f381f76e8333097dc6dc418c4bdd5","tid":303200,"uid":77134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:45:16.000Z","msg":"第一次撘飛機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi